OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNew police powers to tackle
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fslow-walking protests      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Police in England and Wales are to be  
OL,6, given new powers to tackle "disruptive"
OL,7, slow walking used by protesters to     
OL,8, block roads.                           
OL,10,FThe new legislation would give officers
OL,11,Fmore leeway to intervene when          
OL,12,Fprotesters attempt to block roads by   
OL,13,Fslow marching.                         
OL,15,FIt will need to be approved by         
OL,16,FParliament before it comes into force. 
OL,18,FJust Stop Oil, Insulate Britain and    
OL,19,FExtinction Rebellion are among the     
OL,20,Fgroups to have used the tactic.        
